Author: shortLavender
Text: I have totally done the EXACT same thing! Except it wasn't to a therapist when I said it. And I also thought the same thing, like why the eff did I just say that out loud?!?! I got a weird look, but I was able to brush it off since it wasn't a therapist. You can always say it's just a nervous thing or fidgity thing you.? Good luck.
